ing: 6 cups tightly packed chopped romaine lettuce
1 pound cooked boneless skinless chicken breasts, cut into strips
1/2 cup CRACKER BARREL Finely Shredded 100% Parmesan Cheese
des: "A classic recipe for a reason, this chicken Caesar salad is delicious and satisfying. Crunchy romaine, creamy dressing, tender chicken and savoury cheese come together for a tasty favourite."
ins:
Cover 4 plates with lettuce.
Top with all remaining ingredients except dressing.
Drizzle with dressing just before serving.
